---
title: Farmhouse Vegetable Gratin with Borlotti Beans and Crunchy Mozzarella Topping
description: What’s in a name? When it comes to naming our recipes it’s a pretty simple case of imagining where you might eat this dish if you weren’t in your kitchen. We quite fancied that we’d eat this in a cosy little cottage on a hilltop in the south of France.
